  rounds:
  - victimMessage: "Xe SH h\u1EA3i quan thanh l\xFD c\xF2n ko ad \u01A1i? Cho e xin
      gi\xE1."
    scriptToType: Da xe sh y nguyen ban gia hai muoi trieu con mot chiec.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "Gi\u1EA5y t\u1EDD h\u1EE3p l\u1EC7 \u0111i \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng
      ko? M\xECnh s\u1EE3 hugo b\u1EBF l\u1EAFm."
    scriptToType: Bao di duong thoai mai, co ca the nganh chong tich thu.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 1
    distractionMessage: "Ch\xE9m gi\xF3 uy t\xEDn l\xEAn! Nh\u1EAFn l\u1EA5p l\u1EEDng
      n\xF3 ch\u1EA1y m\u1EA5t \u0111\u1EA5y!"
  - victimMessage: "M\xECnh mu\u1ED1n l\xEAn b\xE3i xem xe tr\u1EF1c ti\u1EBFp \u0111c
      ko ad?"
    scriptToType: Bai xe nam trong khu quan su nen khong vao duoc.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "Ok v\u1EADy c\u1ECDc tr\u01B0\u1EDBc bao nhi\xEAu \u0111\u1EC3
      m ship xe v\u1EC1 t\u1EADn nh\xE0?"
    scriptToType: Anh coc truoc muoi trieu roi nhan vien se danh xe xuong.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "Done nha ad! M\xECnh ck 10 c\u1EE7 r\u1ED3i, test xe ok thanh
